                    <msContents>
                        <summary>The Gospel of John. The name of the scribe
                            ሲሎንዲስ occurs on ff. <locus target="#129v">129v</locus> and <locus target="#131r">131r</locus>. A prayer for the scribe is
                            included at the end of the manuscript on f. 129r. On f. 129v another
                            scribe Akliä Giyorgis, added the benediction, "Simeon, by name Papas but
                            not in practice." </summary>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1r" to="131r">1r-131r</locus>
                            <title>The Gospel of John</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#1r">1r</locus> ብስራተ፡አብ፡ትሩፍ፡ራድእ፡ተናጋፊ፡
                                በመለኮት፡ዮሐንስ፡ወንጌላዊ፡ወልደ፡ዘብዴዎስ፡ፍቁረ፡እግዚእነ፡ኢየ
                                ሱስ፡ክርስቶስ፡በረከቱ፡የህሉ፡ምስለ፡ፍቁሩ፡ሲሎንዲስ፡ለዓለመ፡ዓለም፡ኣሜ።</explicit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez"><locus target="#129v">129v</locus>
                                ወኵሉ፡ቃሉ፡ለወንጌለ፡ጽድቅ፡ውእቱ፡እምጥ ንቱ፡እስከ፡ተፍጻሜቱ፡ ለሊሁ፡ ወልድ፡ተናገረ።</explicit>
                            <note>See Or. 1881</note>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
